{
  "dialogue": {
    "Oh. You just moved in, right? Cool.": ["Introduction"],
    "Out of all the places you could live, you chose Pelican Town?": [
      "Introduction_sv1"
    ],
    "Oh, really? I wasn't expecting this. It looks great, though. Thank you.": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive"
    ],
    "Uhh... well, I appreciate the thought.": ["AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative"],
    "Don't make fun of me... but I've never been in a relationship like this before.": [
      "dating_Sebastian_male_farmer"
    ],
    "Don't make fun of me... but I've never really had a girlfriend before.": [
      "dating_Sebastian_female_farmer"
    ],
    "Hey... you look great.": ["dating_Sebastian_memory_oneday"],
    "I've been thinking about you all day...": [
      "dating_Sebastian_memory_oneday_sv1"
    ],
    "Hey... It's been a year since we started dating, remember?": [
      "dating_Sebastian_memory_oneyear"
    ],
    "It's been the best year of my life...": [
      "dating_Sebastian_memory_oneyear_sv1"
    ],
    "Oh yeah? ... Alright, I will.": ["FlowerDance_Accept"],
    "Heh... maybe this festival isn't so bad.": ["FlowerDance_Accept_sv1"],
    "Demetrius has been all wound up because of the wedding, it's been pretty tense around the house.": [
      "married_Maru"
    ],
    "My mom's freaking out, but I'm actually kind of enjoying this. I bet the frogs are going wild out there!": [
      "GreenRain"
    ],
    "I'm gonna stay here to try and keep her calm, though.": ["GreenRain_sv1"],
    "I was hoping this weather would come back. It makes me appreciate the summer a little more.": [
      "GreenRain_2"
    ],
    "The show went well. I was kind of nervous beforehand, but once we went up on stage I just kinda got into the zone.": [
      "eventSeen_4081148"
    ],
    "Is that obsidian? This is exactly what I've been looking for... I'm gonna see if I can shape it into a dagger.": [
      "AcceptGift_575"
    ],
    "Hey, thank you. I'll drink this when the sky gets dark.": [
      "AcceptGift_StardropTea"
    ],
    "What are you trying to say... I need to work out?": [
      "AcceptGift_Book_Defense"
    ],
    "Well, I'm more of a 'nimble' guy... Maybe I'll read the first half.": [
      "AcceptGift_Book_Defense_sv1"
    ],
    "I really love this. How did you know?": ["AcceptGift_227_chance_1"],
    "Mmm... once you get used to eating raw fish, it becomes really addictive.": [
      "AcceptGift_227_chance_2"
    ],
    "Whoa... This egg speaks to me... I'll put it on my desk. Thanks!": [
      "AcceptGift_305_chance_1"
    ],
    "Hmm... I wonder, if I put this under my pillow, will it hatch? Hehe... only one way to find out.": [
      "AcceptGift_305_chance_2"
    ],
    "You brought me soup? That's really nice of you.": ["AcceptGift_236"],
    "This one brings back a lot of memories...": ["AcceptGift_236_sv1"],
    "Hey, that's a frog egg! I'll see if I can get it to hatch. Thanks!": [
      "AcceptGift_FrogEgg"
    ],
    "I'm glad the path to the railroad tracks is open again.": [
      "firstVisit_Railroad"
    ],
    "I like going up there when I feel like being alone.": [
      "firstVisit_Railroad_sv1"
    ],
    "...Which is often.": ["firstVisit_Railroad_sv2"],
    "I liked the boat ride. At one point you couldn't see any land at all..": [
      "Resort_Entering"
    ],
    "I'm ready to get back home.": ["Resort_Leaving"],
    "The beach is nice, but I don't love the crowds.": ["Resort"],
    "You think Willy would let me lug a jet ski out here?": ["Resort_Shore"],
    "...Nah.": ["Resort_Shore_sv1"],
    "...Now, if I were a tropical frog, where would I hide...": [
      "Resort_Wander"
    ],
    "I bet this place looks pretty cool in the rain.": ["Resort_Wander_2"],
    "It's good to get away from the computer and see the real world sometimes. I forget how nice it can be.": [
      "Resort_Towel"
    ],
    "I usually wear black, but in this heat...": ["Resort_Bar"],
    "Ugh... do we have to? Alright.": ["FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse"],
    "No... There's someone else I want to dance with.": ["FlowerDance_Decline"],
    "Why do you keep bothering me? I'm trying to forget about you.": [
      "divorced"
    ],
    "I don't want to see you for a while.": ["dumped_Guys"],
    "... alright...": ["breakUp"],
    "I guess I'll see you around, then...": ["breakUp_sv1"],
    "Hey...": ["secondChance_Guys", "winter_Tue4"],
    "Um... need something?": ["Mon"],
    "If I just disappeared would it really matter?": ["Mon4"],
    "I was thinking... people are like stones skipping over the water.": [
      "Tue"
    ],
    "Eventually we're going to sink.": ["Tue_sv1"],
    "Sam's really outgoing, so when we hang out he does most of the talking.": [
      "Tue6_mw"
    ],
    "That's fine with me!": ["Tue6_mw_sv1"],
    "Imagine if Sam was as reserved as I am... we'd hang out and never say a word.": [
      "Tue6_mw_sv1"
    ],
    "Some people are talkers, others are listeners. I'm more of a listener.": [
      "Tue6_mw_sv2"
    ],
    "What am I going to do today?": ["Wed"],
    "Probably nothing.": ["Wed_sv1"],
    "Sam is probably my only friend in this town.": ["Wed2"],
    "Well, Abby is nice too, but...": ["Wed2_sv1"],
    "Umm.. never mind.": ["Wed2_sv2"],
    "Sam is probably my only friend in this town, anymore...": [
      "Wed2_inlaw_Abigail"
    ],
    "You and Sam are probably my only friends in this town.": ["Wed6"],
    "I dunno where I'd be without you... probably in a ditch somewhere.": [
      "Wed10"
    ],
    "I snuck into the caves last night and got a nasty cut from a rock crab. Don't tell anyone, okay?": [
      "Thu_chance_1"
    ],
    "Hi.": ["Thu_chance_2"],
    "...want something?": ["Thu_sv1"],
    "I come here for the peace and quiet.": ["Mountain_47_23"],
    "Why does everyone like Maru so much? Sure, she's smart and friendly, but don't they realize it's all just an attention-grabbing scam?": [
      "Thu4"
    ],
    "Sorry...": ["Thu4_sv1"],
    "Could you picture someone like me living on a farm? It seems ridiculous.": [
      "Thu6"
    ],
    "Hey... How are things going on the farm?": ["Thu8_query_1"],
    "Same old routine, huh? Yeah, I know a thing or two about that...": [
      "Thu8_query_1_sv1"
    ],
    "Could you picture me living on a farm?": ["Thu8_query_2"],
    "It seems ridiculous, but I have been thinking about it lately.": [
      "Thu8_query_2_sv1"
    ],
    "Uh... I don't really know you.": ["Fri"],
    "*sigh*... If gas wasn't so expensive I'd ride my motorcycle to the city today.": [
      "Fri2"
    ],
    "So what do you do when you aren't working?": ["Fri2_sv1"],
    "Hey, if you're bored feel free to hang out in my room...": [
      "Fri_old_prereq_1"
    ],
    "You probably prefer the small-town life, huh?": ["Fri_old_prereq_2"],
    "Oh yeah? Well, did you read the new 'Cave Saga X'? I won't spoil it for you, but oh man...": [
      "Fri_good"
    ],
    "Oh yea? Hmm... Not really my thing, but everyone's different I guess.": [
      "Fri_bad"
    ],
    "What? I didn't hear you... I'm busy thinking about something.": ["Sat"],
    "What do you want?": ["Sat_sv1"],
    "You know, I should be doing something productive right now. I just lose focus too fast...": [
      "Sat2"
    ],
    "Maybe I should drink more coffee?": ["Sat2_sv1"],
    "Hey. Your name is @, right?": ["Sun"],
    "Having a good weekend? ...nice.": ["Sun2"],
    "I usually stay inside, but I do go to the beach now and then.": ["Sun4"],
    "Pretty much only when it's raining, though.": ["Sun4_sv1"],
    "For some reason, staring off into the bleak horizon makes me feel... I dunno. Like it's worthwhile to keep pushing on, I guess.": [
      "Sun4_sv2"
    ],
    "What's new?": ["Fri8"],
    "I'll be at the saloon tonight destroying Sam at pool again.": ["Fri8_sv1"],
    "I was just thinking about you...": ["Sun10"],
    "Okay, that'll work.": ["Event_game1"],
    "Good choice. That works well with my role.": ["Event_game2"],
    "Not so fast! I want to know what it is.": ["Event_cave1"],
    "Really? It was making a lot of noise!": ["Event_cave2"],
    "It's too dangerous without a sword. But I like your sense of adventure.": [
      "Event_cave3"
    ],
    "Great.": ["event_garage1"],
    "Okay... Never mind then.": ["event_garage2"],
    "Don't worry, I'll make sure to show you the ropes before I let you do anything dangerous.": [
      "event_garage3_male_farmer"
    ],
    "There's no need to worry... I'll make sure you're safe.": [
      "event_garage3_female_farmer"
    ],
    "Hmm... Not exactly how I'd put it but, yeah.": ["event_city1"],
    "Yea... That's exactly how I feel, too.": ["event_city2"],
    "Oh... Well maybe this wasn't the right place to bring you, then. I thought you'd see the beauty in it.": [
      "event_city3"
    ],
    "Ugh... You sound like my Mom.": ["event_city4"],
    "...*sigh*": ["event_city4_sv1"],
    "You're right, though. I'm addicted to these things, it's not good.": [
      "event_city4_sv2"
    ],
    "Everyone is so happy in the sun. I don't get it.": ["summer_Mon"],
    "Everyone is so happy when it's sunny out...": ["summer_Mon6_mw"],
    "Different people like different things, I guess.": ["summer_Mon6_mw_sv1"],
    "Most people like the sun, huh?": ["summer_Mon6_mw_sv1"],
    "I guess you do need a minimum amount of vitamin D...": [
      "summer_Mon6_mw_sv2"
    ],
    "I'm looking forward to the cold, damp season. I feel more at home.": [
      "summer_Tue"
    ],
    "I'm looking forward to the cold, damp season. Channeling my inner toad, I guess.": [
      "summer_Tue4"
    ],
    "What's the point of going outside? I've already seen it all.": [
      "summer_Wed"
    ],
    "If you're depressed, everything seems stupid. But if you're feeling positive, then even the most mundane things will make you happy.": [
      "summer_Wed6"
    ],
    "How do you stay positive long term? I have no idea.": ["summer_Wed6_sv1"],
    "...Maybe I'll figure it out some day.": ["summer_Wed6_sv2"],
    "Why am I grinning? I guess I've been unusually happy lately...": [
      "summer_Wed10"
    ],
    "I definitely don't want to go swimming, if that's what you're going to ask.": [
      "summer_Thu"
    ],
    "Oh, you just stopped to say hi? Sorry.": ["summer_Thu_sv1"],
    "If you ever wanted to go swimming... I guess I'd do it.": ["summer_Thu10"],
    "The temperature only starts to get comfortable at night.": [
      "summer_Mountain_58_35_chance_1"
    ],
    "It always seems to stay a little cooler by the lake.": [
      "summer_Mountain_58_35_chance_2"
    ],
    "Oh, hey. *yawn*... sorry.": ["summer_Fri"],
    "Hey, I'm glad you stopped by.": ["summer_Fri6"],
    "How have you been coping with this heat?": ["summer_Fri6_sv1"],
    "I hope we're not having mushroom casserole tonight...": ["summer_Sat_mw"],
    "Oh no, is it cave carrot tacos night? ...*groan*": ["summer_Sat_mw_sv1"],
    "I'm not too big on festivals. Lots of commotion, too much social interaction... More stress than fun, if you ask me.": [
      "spring_12"
    ],
    "Ugh... Tomorrow is the worst festival of the year by a mile. Just wait and see how stupid I look during the flower dance.": [
      "spring_23"
    ],
    "Are you looking forward to the Spirit's Eve festival? It's probably my favorite.": [
      "fall_20"
    ],
    "The Spirit's Eve festival is tomorrow. I really hope they have those skeletons on display again this year.": [
      "fall_26"
    ],
    "I almost feel like they're my friends at this point.": ["fall_26_sv1"],
    "Hehe... It might be funny to put something disgusting in the potluck soup tomorrow. Just don't poison anyone.": [
      "summer_10"
    ],
    "Why ruin the potluck? Hmm... I guess some people feel liberated when the rigid structures of society break down a little. Maybe I'm weird.": [
      "summer_10_sv1"
    ],
    "Tomorrow we'll all be gathering at the docks to see the migration of the moonlight jellies. I think it starts at ten o'clock.": [
      "summer_27"
    ],
    "It's the eve of the winter star today. Better make sure you've got an empty stomach for the feast tomorrow.": [
      "winter_24"
    ],
    "I usually only go outside after dark. Does that sound weird to you?": [
      "summer_Sun"
    ],
    "Last night, I saw a group of bats flying around near the lake.": [
      "summer_Sun4"
    ],
    "I guess maybe they are feeding on the mosquitoes this time of year?": [
      "summer_Sun4_sv1"
    ],
    "So... it's the big harvest season, isn't it?": ["fall_Mon"],
    "You're probably making a lot of money on your farm, huh?": ["fall_Mon4"],
    "I guess I should get a job soon...": ["fall_Mon4_sv1"],
    "Pumpkin spice this... pumpkin spice that... man, I do get sick of these seasonal fads.": [
      "fall_Tue"
    ],
    "Who does Demetrius think he is, telling me what to do? He's not even my real father.": [
      "fall_Tue6"
    ],
    "I've always felt like an underdog. But the challenge will just make me stronger.": [
      "fall_Tue10"
    ],
    "*yawn*... what time is it? I think I slept too much last night.": [
      "fall_Wed"
    ],
    "I'm glad you showed up. I was starting to get bored.": ["fall_Wed8"],
    "Now I feel a lot more energetic, believe it or not.": ["fall_Wed8_sv1"],
    "My room might be a little less depressing if I had a window...": [
      "fall_Thu"
    ],
    "*yawn*... I was up until 3 reading this new book...": ["fall_Fri"],
    "Do you read, @?": ["fall_Fri_sv1"],
    "You probably wouldn't like it.": ["fall_Fri_old_prereq_1"],
    "I think you'd like it.": ["fall_Fri_old_prereq_2"],
    "Hey, me too. There's nothing like a good fiction to push the boundaries of the imagination.": [
      "fall_Fri_good"
    ],
    "Huh. Sounds boring.": ["fall_Fri_bad"],
    "I've been reading a book about a farmer. Reminds me a lot of you, actually.": [
      "fall_Fri6"
    ],
    "Sorry if that creeps you out.": ["fall_Fri6_sv1"],
    "I was *this* close to moping in bed the entire day. Kinda wish I had, now.": [
      "fall_Sat"
    ],
    "The sun is coming out less and less these days... wonderful.": [
      "fall_Sun"
    ],
    "I'm enjoying this gloomy weather... although I have to say, it's a little cold.": [
      "winter_Mon"
    ],
    "Nothing surprises me anymore... nothing makes me laugh.": ["winter_Mon4"],
    "Yeah, I know... I'm being a little dramatic.": ["winter_Mon4_sv1"],
    "Do you ever think back on your old self with shame and embarrassment?": [
      "winter_Mon8"
    ],
    "I guess it's just part of growing up.": ["winter_Mon8_sv1"],
    "Hmm... I don't really have anything to say. I still don't know you very well.": [
      "winter_Tue"
    ],
    "It's hard to think of new things to talk about, sometimes. Even after you know someone.": [
      "winter_Tue4_sv1"
    ],
    "...Sorry.": ["winter_Tue4_sv2"],
    "I was so close to screaming at Mom for throwing away my old comic collection... But something stopped me.": [
      "winter_Tue6"
    ],
    "Hmm... with age comes wisdom.": ["winter_Tue6_sv1"],
    "You came here to see me?": ["winter_Tue10"],
    "...": ["winter_Tue10_sv1"],
    "%Sebastian seems lost in thought...": ["winter_Wed"],
    "Hey, don't let me stop you from getting your work done.": ["winter_Wed4"],
    "If you aren't busy I don't mind if you stick around.": ["winter_Wed4_sv1"],
    "I wonder what's for dinner tonight... *grumble*": ["winter_Thu"],
    "I should learn how to cook. That would be useful.": ["winter_Thu6"],
    "It's fun to live so close to the train tracks. It's a reminder that there's a big world out there.": [
      "winter_Fri"
    ],
    "When I was younger I'd run out to the railroad whenever I heard a train coming.": [
      "winter_Fri8"
    ],
    "Whatever happened to those days...? *sigh*": ["winter_Fri8_sv1"],
    "The frogs aren't very happy in winter.": ["winter_Sat_mw"],
    "Poor little guys.": ["winter_Sat_mw_sv1"],
    "I wonder what the frogs do in winter? Do they just become frozen and then thaw out in spring?": [
      "winter_Sat_mw_sv1"
    ],
    "I like winter but I do feel bad for all the cold animals out there.": [
      "winter_Sat6"
    ],
    "I guess they're used to it, though... like me.": ["winter_Sat6_sv1"],
    "I built a snowgoon but Demetrius made me get rid of it.": ["winter_Sun"],
    "What's his problem?": ["winter_Sun_sv1"],
    "I built a snowgoon but Demetrius made me get rid of it... yet Maru's cute little snowman goes unharmed!": [
      "winter_Sun6"
    ],
    "Ridiculous.": ["winter_Sun6_sv1"]
  },
  "marriage_dialogue": {
    "Finally... some heavy rain. I get bored of sunny weather easily.": [
      "Rainy_Day_0"
    ],
    "Hey. I was just thinking about my old room in the basement. I felt comfortable there, but this is a lot more interesting. And I don't miss the smell...": [
      "Rainy_Day_1"
    ],
    "I felt kind of embarrassed living in my mom's house for so long.": [
      "Rainy_Day_1_sv1"
    ],
    "Hey. I couldn't sleep last night so I took a walk to the caves. I found this... want it?": [
      "Rainy_Day_2"
    ],
    "I just have trouble sleeping sometimes, it has nothing to do with you. I love you.": [
      "Rainy_Day_2_sv1"
    ],
    "Seems like a pretty good day to just lay around, maybe read a book or something... what do you think?": [
      "Rainy_Day_3"
    ],
    "Hey, another rainy day... perfect.": ["Rainy_Day_4"],
    "You look cold... here, come closer.": ["Rainy_Day_4_sv1"],
    "I'm trying my best to quit smoking now that we're married... I don't wanna die on you. It's a bad habit.": [
      "Rainy_Night_0"
    ],
    "I want to have a future together.": ["Rainy_Night_0_sv1"],
    "Need something? I'll just be over here working on my bike for a while.": [
      "patio_Sebastian"
    ],
    "I did some work on the laptop today. I was actually brainstorming some ideas for a game I want to make.": [
      "Rainy_Night_1"
    ],
    "With your farming income, I can afford to do what I want with my life. It's pretty amazing. Thank you.": [
      "Rainy_Night_1_sv1"
    ],
    "Sorry, I didn't make any dinner. We might have a frozen pizza in the fridge or something.": [
      "Rainy_Night_2"
    ],
    "I dunno, my mind was elsewhere. It's hard to remember to do chores...": [
      "Rainy_Night_2_sv1"
    ],
    "How was your day? Did you slay any monsters?": ["Rainy_Night_3"],
    "It feels good to take out your aggression now and then, doesn't it?": [
      "Rainy_Night_3_sv1"
    ],
    "Maybe a witch will visit us tonight? Hah.. if only life was that interesting...": [
      "Rainy_Night_4"
    ],
    "The older I get, the less I'm drawn to the city. It had a certain mystique to it, once. But it turns out that was just a romantic fantasy.": [
      "Indoor_Day_0"
    ],
    "The city's so busy, so full of people... I don't belong there. I'm a loner.": [
      "Indoor_Day_0_sv1"
    ],
    "Hey... want some coffee?": ["Indoor_Day_1"],
    "I needed some... woke up early from a nightmare and I just couldn't fall back asleep.": [
      "Indoor_Day_1_sv1"
    ],
    "I couldn't sleep last night so I went for a night ride on the motorcycle.": [
      "Indoor_Day_2"
    ],
    "I need to stay independent, even though we're married. That's just how I am. I still love you, though.": [
      "Indoor_Day_2_sv1"
    ],
    "Hey. How'd you sleep last night? I heard you mumbling.": ["Indoor_Day_3"],
    "You seemed scared, but I have to admit... it was kind of cute.": [
      "Indoor_Day_3_sv1"
    ],
    "Living here with you is teaching me to come out of my shell a little bit. I think it's good for me.": [
      "Indoor_Day_4"
    ],
    "Hey. I just hung out around the house, today. Nothing interesting...": [
      "Indoor_Night_0"
    ],
    "...": ["Indoor_Night_0_sv1"],
    "The view from our house is perfect. You can see the sun setting over Pelican Town from the front porch.": [
      "Indoor_Night_0_sv2"
    ],
    "Maybe I drank too much coffee... I don't feel very tired.": [
      "Indoor_Night_1"
    ],
    "I'm still trying to adjust to the farm schedule. I used to stay up until 5am and sleep in until 2pm, sometimes.": [
      "Indoor_Night_1_sv1"
    ],
    "It's really cool to have our own place. I can do whatever I feel like and not have people nagging at me all the time.": [
      "Indoor_Night_2"
    ],
    "I'm sure Maru's happy that I'm gone.": ["Indoor_Night_2_sv1"],
    "I spotted a bat out the window earlier. It's kind of hard to see, but if you stay focused you can often catch them flittering about. They're out there.": [
      "Indoor_Night_3"
    ],
    "I often felt unappreciated back home... but here I feel like I really belong. Thanks for making me feel welcome, @.": [
      "Indoor_Night_4"
    ],
    "I feel like I want to do something today... but I'm not sure what. Do you ever have that problem, @?": [
      "Outdoor_0"
    ],
    "Hmm... sometimes I have to force myself to stay outside for health.": [
      "Outdoor_1"
    ],
    "I dunno what it is, but I like being indoors. Maybe I'm just so used to my dark basement.": [
      "Outdoor_1_sv1"
    ],
    "I'll just watch you from here.": ["Outdoor_2"],
    "I enjoy watching you.": ["Outdoor_2_sv1"],
    "I don't want to get soft now that I'm a married guy. Maybe I should start eating more hot pepper and working out?": [
      "Outdoor_3"
    ],
    "Just an idea...": ["Outdoor_3_sv1"],
    "We should raise more slimes... In big quantities they can be pretty profitable. And they're so easy to raise.": [
      "Outdoor_4"
    ],
    "Also, different colored slimes produce different items. I dunno, I think it'd be kind of a fun hobby for us.": [
      "Outdoor_4_sv1"
    ],
    "I'm still getting used to being a father. Don't worry, I'll take good care of %kid1! It's just... something new.": [
      "OneKid_0"
    ],
    "Maybe when %kid1 is a little older, I'll get a sidecar for the bike and we can all go for a ride.": [
      "OneKid_1"
    ],
    "Have you smelled %kid1? Maybe it's time for a bath...": ["OneKid_3"],
    "Don't worry, I already fed the kids... %kid2 spilled the chocolate milk all over my shirt again.": [
      "TwoKids_0"
    ],
    "I hope %kid1 and %kid2 are nice to each other. Maru and I always fought as kids.": [
      "TwoKids_1"
    ],
    "If I think back on it, it was mostly my fault...": ["TwoKids_1_sv1"],
    "I've had this recurring dream that %kid2 is wearing a shadow shaman costume and sitting on a glowing pumpkin. Weird, huh?": [
      "TwoKids_2"
    ],
    "We've come a long way, @. Look at our family. To be honest, I never really thought I'd end up in this situation.": [
      "TwoKids_3"
    ],
    "Now that I'm here, I like it...": ["TwoKids_3_sv1"],
    "Hey. Look at me. Never forget that I love you... you're everything to me.": [
      "Good_0"
    ],
    "Now go make us some money.": ["Good_0_sv1"],
    "Hey... come here. You look great today.": ["Good_1"],
    "You always look great, even after slopping around in the yard all day.": [
      "Good_2"
    ],
    "I don't often show it, but I'm really happy that I'm your husband. Marrying you was the best decision I ever made.": [
      "Good_3"
    ],
    "You don't ever have to worry about me. I like to spend a lot of time alone.": [
      "Good_4"
    ],
    "Sometimes I feel so angry... but when you show up I always start to calm down.": [
      "Good_5"
    ],
    "Maybe I'll mellow out with age.": ["Good_5_sv1"],
    "I know you're tough, but I still worry about you, sometimes. Don't ever go monster hunting without a life elixir and some sturdy boots, okay?": [
